content: Screen goes black in middle of match won't open back up. You have to completely close the game and restart all the way back over. Doesn't even save. You Should give everyone that you have charged for this game a refund.

Would love to rate 5 but within an hour of playing the AI hijacked the game in the middle of my turn, twice, and then froze in the middle of the AI turn with no way to save my progress. You dev's have put out enough games that you should be at least competent by now. Do you beta test at all? Anybody reading this should pass til this buggy mess is fixed.
